      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. This example showcases exceptional throttle response from its individual throttle bodies and linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis benefits from a reinforced subframe and updated bushings, maintaining the precise handling characteristics of the M-tuned MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension. The limited-slip differential provides optimal traction through corners, while recent maintenance\u2014including a comprehensive double-VANOS service and valve adjustment\u2014ensures peak performance. A high-integrity driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
