      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features, from the panoramic sunroof to the dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced every 5,000 miles with full synthetic oil, and the most recent inspection confirmed that the brake pads and rotors have significant life remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision. It sits on a set of high-performance tires with approximately 70% tread depth. This is a solid, honest car that has many miles of dependable service left to offer. Clear title in hand and ready for its next owner.",
